" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係咁講既<br />\n可以無師自通架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢師父以前都幾勁<br />\n冇記錯當年好似係英國最年輕米芝蓮3星廚<br />\n不過而家就幫家樂派sell 濃湯寶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加少少橄欖油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAdd little Oliver oil <br />\n之後狂倒<br />\n呢個gap笑一百次都唔點</blockquote><br />\n講到爛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有中文譒譯既片一定有台仔講哩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n公道講佢對一般家庭用濃湯寶之類既觀點好似未幫Knorr之前都有講過<br />\n<br />\n一般家庭本冇可能用幾個鐘自己煲stocking,有限時間同錢下用現成野好合理"},{"pid":"c5910e3e75a35c48984df63122b4152eeea60181","tid":192443,"uid":4973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:57:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無巴打順手睇埋gordon果四集地獄廚神之監獄風雲，係外國監獄帶住一隊囚犯，由佢地乜都唔識，亳無紀律，每一兩分鐘都要同人吵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，帶到最後佢地成大事岀黎。真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感動個程度係我平時睇d虐心電影都係眼淚在心裏流，睇完呢個竟然要忍住唔流先無喊到岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廚神當之無愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇呢輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有睇 YouTube有齊</blockquote><br />\n好好睇 睇到Gordon既另一面 佢幫另一個犯人求情 比佢返去廚房 果幾幕都幾感動</blockquote><br />\n無記錯佢親兄弟都係吸毒<br />\n所以佢感受好深<br />\n<br />\n佢既形象係美國要效果做出黎<br />\n佢係英國既節目係正常好多，係一個好風趣幽默既人黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢老豆好似都係監躉<br />\n佢監倉嗰個系列係幾正<br />\n不過最失敗係帶咗佢個女助手入去揸旗<br />\n有時Gordon 又會嚟唔到<br />\n留返班監躉同條女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9c5fa688634c8356da742e9e1a9e6d979b5e57","tid":192443,"uid":81817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無巴打順手睇埋gordon果四集地獄廚神之監獄風雲，係外國監獄帶住一隊囚犯，由佢地乜都唔識，亳無紀律，每一兩分鐘都要同人吵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，帶到最後佢地成大事岀黎。真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感動個程度係我平時睇d虐心電影都係眼淚在心裏流，睇完呢個竟然要忍住唔流先無喊到岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廚神當之無愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇呢輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有睇 YouTube有齊</blockquote><br />\n好好睇 睇到Gordon既另一面 佢幫另一個犯人求情 比佢返去廚房 果幾幕都幾感動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係最後呢班犯得兩個真改過自新<br />\n其他人繼續重覆犯罪<br />\n因為成效不大，唔係應該會有第二季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ed6da7cb3946e4f8778394b798a45e7f6ecc4d","tid":192443,"uid":4973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔通一生出黎就識煮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係咁講既<br />\n可以無師自通架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢師父以前都幾勁<br />\n冇記錯當年好似係英國最年輕米芝蓮3星廚<br />\n不過而家就幫家樂派sell 濃湯寶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加少少橄欖油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAdd little Oliver oil <br />\n之後狂倒<br />\n呢個gap笑一百次都唔點</bloc