s work"},{"pid":"a4b764ef37c75d911ef2f6f069d2be032ec7889f","tid":192443,"uid":76412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔通一生出黎就識煮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係咁講既<br />\n可以無師自通架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢師父以前都幾勁<br />\n冇記錯當年好似係英國最年輕米芝蓮3星廚<br />\n不過而家就幫家樂派sell 濃湯寶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAdd Little Oliver oil <br />\n之後38歲唔要三星<br />\n打理返屋企就算</blockquote><br />\n名師出高徒真係..<br />\n佢拎住3星之後 GORDAN就緊隨住師父拎2星</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Gordon Ramsay 連講嘢都學足佢師父<br />\n例如: Let your knife do the work<br />\n<br />\n但係佢哋好似炒大鑊<br />\n據聞話Gordon Ramsay 帶咗隊攝製隊偷影佢師父婚禮<br />\n搞到佢師父唔happy, 仲告埋上庭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87afa74a001205bf765e8795b92d632078e19090","tid":192443,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無巴打順手睇埋gordon果四集地獄廚神之監獄風雲，係外國監獄帶住一隊囚犯，由佢地乜都唔識，亳無紀律，每一兩分鐘都要同人吵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，帶到最後佢地成大事岀黎。真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />